high_descs: Turn around and walk to table.  Turn right and face shelves with apples on it.
Pick up knife off table, from between two apples.
Turn right, then turn left to face sink.
Place knife in sink, to the left of the pear and potato, diagonal on the spoon.  Turn water on, turn water off, drain water.  Pick up knife.
Move back to shelf at the end of the counter by making three right hand turns.
Place knife on table, lying across both apples.
anns.task_desc: Wash knife and return to shelf.

high_descs: walk forward a few steps, turn right, walk across the room, turn right to face the small brown table
pick up the knife that is on the brown table
turn right, walk a few steps forward, turn left to face the sink
put the knife in the sink, turn the water on, turn it off, take the knife out of the sink
turn around, take a couple steps, turn right, take a couple steps, turn right to face the small brown table
put the knife on to the brown table
anns.task_desc: wash a knife to put it away

high_descs: Turn to the right and then the right again to find the black table.
Pick up the knife that is in between the two apples.
Take the knife and move a few steps to the right towards the sink.
Place the knife in the sink, turn the water on and off. Pick up the knife from the sink.
Carry the knife and move a bit to the left to find the black table again.
Place the knife standing up in front of the apples.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a knife and place it on the table.
